put/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/DateConverter.java**\n- Utility class for date/time conversions\n- Uses `LocalDate` and `LocalDateTime`\n\n### Domain Model - Cargo (11 files)\n\n**12-22**: Files include:\n- `TransportStatus.java` - Enum with states: NOT_RECEIVED, IN_PORT, ONBOARD_CARRIER, CLAIMED, UNKNOWN\n- `TrackingId.java` - JPA `@Embeddable` value object\n- `RoutingStatus.java` - Enum: NOT_ROUTED, ROUTED, MISROUTED\n- `RouteSpecification.java` - `@Embeddable` specification pattern\n- `CargoRepository.java` - Repository interface\n- `Delivery.java` - Complex `@Embeddable` with cargo delivery state\n- `HandlingActivity.java` - `@Embeddable` for handling activities\n- `Itinerary.java` - `@Embeddable` with legs collection\n- `Cargo.java` - Main `@Entity` aggregate root with `@NamedQuery` annotations\n- `Leg.java` - `@Entity` representing route leg\n\n### Domain Model - Voyage (7 files)\n\n**23-29**: Files include:\n- `VoyageNumber.java` - `@Embeddable` value object\n- `Voyage.java` - `@Entity` with Builder pattern\n- `SampleVoyages.java` - Sample data constants\n- `CarrierMovement.java` - `@Entity` for carrier movements\n- `Schedule.java` - `@Embeddable` with carrier movements\n- `VoyageRepository.java` - Repository interface\n\n### Domain Model - Location (4 files)\n\n**30-33**: Files include:\n- `UnLocode.java` - `@Embeddable` with regex validation\n- `SampleLocations.java` - Sample location constants\n- `Location.java` - `@Entity` with UN location codes\n- `LocationRepository.java` - Repository interface\n\n### Domain Model - Handling (8 files)\n\n**34-41**: Files include:\n- Exception classes: `UnknownVoyageException`, `UnknownLocationException`, `UnknownCargoException`, `CannotCreateHandlingEventException`\n- `HandlingHistory.java` - Value object for handling history\n- `HandlingEventRepository.java` - Repository interface\n- `HandlingEventFactory.java` - `@ApplicationScoped` factory with `@Inject`\n- `HandlingEvent.java` - Main `@Entity` with Type enum\n\n### Domain Shared (6 files)\n\n**42-47**: Files include:\n- `Specification.java` - Specification pattern interface\n- `OrSpecification.java`, `AndSpecification.java`, `NotSpecification.java` - Specification implementations\n- `AbstractSpecification.java` - Base class\n- `DomainObjectUtils.java` - Null-safe utilities\n\n### Domain Service (1 file)\n\n**48**: `RoutingService.java` - Routing service interface\n\n### Infrastructure - Logging (1 file)\n\n**49. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java**\n- CDI producer for Logger using `@Produces`\n\n### Infrastructure - Persistence (4 files)\n\n**50-53**: JPA repository implementations:\n- `JpaCargoRepository.java` - Uses `@PersistenceContext`, fires CDI events with `@CargoUpdated`\n- `JpaVoyageRepository.java` - `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `JpaLocationRepository.java` - `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `JpaHandlingEventRepository.java` - `@ApplicationScoped`\n\n### Infrastructure - Messaging (6 files)\n\n**54-59**: JMS message-driven beans using `@MessageDriven`:\n- `JmsApplicationEvents.java` - Publishes JMS messages\n- `RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java`\n- `MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java`\n- `HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java`\n- `DeliveredCargoConsumer.java`\n- `CargoHandledConsumer.java`\n\n### Infrastructure - Events (1 file)\n\n**60. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java**\n- CDI `@Qualifier` annotation\n\n### Infrastructure - Routing (1 file)\n\n**61. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/ExternalRoutingService.java**\n- `@Stateless` service calling external REST API\n- Uses JAX-RS client\n\n### Interfaces (3 files)\n\n**62-64**:\n- `FacesConfiguration.java` - Jakarta Faces config\n- `Coordinates.java` - Simple DTO\n- `CoordinatesFactory.java` - Factory for coordinates\n\n### Interfaces - Booking Facade (6 files + 5 assemblers)\n\n**65-75**: DTOs and facade:\n- `BookingServiceFacade.java` - Interface\n- DTOs: `TrackingEvents`, `RouteCandidate`, `Location`, `Leg`, `CargoRoute`, `CargoStatus`\n- Assemblers: `TrackingEventsDtoAssembler`, `ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler`, `LocationDtoAssembler`, `CargoStatusDtoAssembler`, `CargoRouteDtoAssembler`\n- `DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java` - Implementation using `@ApplicationScoped`\n\n### Interfaces - Booking Web (10 files)\n\n**76-85**: JSF backing beans:\n- `Booking.java` - `@FlowScoped(\"booking\")`\n- `Track.java` - `@ViewScoped`\n- `ListCargo.java` - `@RequestScoped`\n- `ItinerarySelection.java` - `@ViewScoped`\n- `ChangeDestinationDialog.java` - `@SessionScoped`\n- `ChangeDestination.java` - `@ViewScoped`\n- `ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java` - `@SessionScoped`\n- `ChangeArrivalDeadline.java` - `@ViewScoped`\n- `CargoDetails.java` - `@RequestScoped`\n\n### Interfaces - Booking SSE (3 files)\n\n**86-88**: Server-Sent Events:\n- `RealtimeCargoTrackingViewAdapter.java` - View adapter\n- `LocationViewAdapter.java` - View adapter\n- `RealtimeCargoTrackingService.java` - `@Singleton` REST service with SSE\n\n### Interfaces - Handling (1 file)\n\n**89. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt.java**\n- Serializable DTO for JMS\n\n### Interfaces - Handling File (7 files)\n\n**90-96**: Batch processing components:\n- `UploadDirectoryScanner.java` - `@Stateless` with `@Schedule` timer\n- `LineParseExceptionListener.java` - Batch `SkipReadListener`\n- `FileProcessorJobListener.java` - Batch `JobListener`\n- `EventLineParseException.java` - Custom exception\n- `EventItemWriter.java` - Batch `AbstractItemWriter` with `@Transactional`\n- `EventItemReader.java` - Batch `AbstractItemReader`\n- `EventFilesCheckpoint.java` - Checkpoint data\n\n### Interfaces - Tracking Web (2 files)\n\n**97-98**:\n- `Track.java` - `@ViewScoped` JSF bean\n- `CargoTrackingViewAdapter.java` - View adapter with inner class\n\n### Pathfinder API (3 files - external module)\n\nAll files are properly annotated and use:\n- **Jakarta EE annotations**: `@Stateless`, `@Singleton`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@ViewScoped`, `@RequestScoped`, `@SessionScoped`, `@FlowScoped`\n- **CDI**: `@Inject`, `@Produces`, `@Qualifier`\n- **JPA**: `@Entity`, `@Embeddable`, `@PersistenceContext`, `@NamedQuery`\n- **JMS**: `@MessageDriven`\n- **Validation**: `@Valid`, `@NotNull`, `@NotEmpty`, `@Pattern`, `@Future`\n- **Batch**: Batch API components\n- **JAX-RS**: `@Path`, `@GET`, `@Produces`, REST endpoints\n- **JSF**: Various JSF backing bean scopes\n\nAll code uses Java 8+ features including LocalDate/LocalDateTime, streams, and lambda expressions."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"82f4a638-406e-4250-9317-12dfec377a3e"}
