{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01TKdeqLm4bzocmSU7PWw7jH","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all the JPA repository implementations from Jakarta EE CDI/EJB to Spring Boot. Here's a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n### 1. JpaCargoRepository.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired` for Logger and ApplicationEventPublisher\n- Replaced CDI `Event<Cargo>` with Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n- Removed imports: `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`, `javax.enterprise.event.Event`, `javax.inject.Inject`\n- Added imports: `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`, `org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisher`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Repository`, `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Changed `cargoUpdated.fireAsync(cargo)` to `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(cargo)`\n- Added `@Transactional` annotation to the `store()` method\n- Kept `@PersistenceContext` unchanged\n\n### 2. JpaVoyageRepository.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepository.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed import: `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Added import: `org.springframework.stereotype.Repository`\n- Kept `@PersistenceContext` unchanged\n\n### 3. JpaLocationRepository.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaLocationRepository.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed import: `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Added import: `org.springframework.stereotype.Repository`\n- Kept `@PersistenceContext` unchanged\n\n### 4. JpaHandlingEventRepository.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaHandlingEventRepository.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed import: `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Added import: `org.springframework.stereotype.Repository`\n- Kept `@PersistenceContext` unchanged\n\n### 5. CargoUpdated.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Simplified to a marker annotation with documentation\n- Removed all CDI-specific annotations and imports (`@Qualifier`, `@Retention`, `@Target`, `javax.inject.Qualifier`)\n- Added comment explaining this is kept for reference but is no longer used as a CDI qualifier in Spring Boot\n\n## Key Migration Points\n\nAll JPA repositories have been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE CDI/EJB to Spring Boot with the following pattern:\n- CDI `@ApplicationScoped` → Spring `@Repository`\n- CDI `@Inject` → Spring `@Autowired`\n- CDI `Event<T>` → Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n- CDI `event.fireAsync()` → Spring `publishEvent()`\n- JPA `@PersistenceContext` remains unchanged (works with both frameworks)\n- Added `@Transactional` to methods that persist data (as needed for Spring transaction management)"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"c0c49d94-2da9-4edc-b37c-66cb12a7d1c1"}
