empt.getType());\n    33→        } catch (CannotCreateHandlingEventException e) {\n    34→            logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Error processing handling event registration\", e);\n    35→        }\n    36→    }\n    37→}\n    38→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Lr8tYg6Hv8qHYAMeW3ZZGs","session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"508ab37b-cd98-4ff8-8ed6-2e8f38a9fe97"}
