{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XZHbRKfioQfMMMxEzpnTdt","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/LineParseExceptionListener.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.handling.file;\n     2→\n     3→/**\n     4→ * Previously a Jakarta Batch SkipReadListener.\n     5→ * In Spring Boot, error handling is done directly in UploadDirectoryScanner.\n     6→ * This class is kept as a placeholder for compilation compatibility.\n     7→ */\n     8→public class LineParseExceptionListener {\n     9→    // No longer needed - error handling in UploadDirectoryScanner\n    10→}\n    11→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Rna5DMppV76Df7QzZauCu5","session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"5e974bdc-dfea-4515-893c-9c43b05a0dbc"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Lr8tYg6Hv8qHYAMeW3ZZGs","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated the JMS messaging infrastructure from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot. Here's a detailed summary of the changes:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI've successfully replaced the JMS-based messaging infrastructure with Spring's Application Event system. All 6 files have been updated to use Spring Boot patterns instead of Jakarta EE.\n\n### Files Modified:\n\n1. **JmsApplicationEvents.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java`)\n   - Removed Jakarta EE annotations: `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject`, `@Resource`\n   - Removed JMS infrastructure: `JMSContext`, `Destination` queues\n   - Added Spring components: `@Component`, `@Autowired`, `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n   - Replaced JMS message sending with Spring event publishing\n   - Added 4 inner event classes: `CargoHandledEvent`, `CargoMisdirectedEvent`, `CargoArrivedEvent`, `HandlingEventRegistrationEvent`\n\n2. **CargoHandledConsumer.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java`)\n   - Removed `@MessageDriven` MDB with activation config\n   - Removed `MessageListener` interface and JMS message handling\n   - Added `@Component` for Spring component scanning\n   - Added `@EventListener` and `@Async` for asynchronous event handling\n   - Simplified event processing without JMS message extraction\n\n3. **HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java`)\n   - Removed MDB configuration and JMS ObjectMessage handling\n   - Added `@EventListener` and `@Async` for event processing\n   - Simplified error handling (removed RuntimeException throw for poison messages)\n   - Direct access to `HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt` from event\n\n4. **MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java`)\n   - Removed `@MessageDriven` and JMS message handling\n   - Added `@Component`, `@EventListener`, and `@Async`\n   - Simplified event processing with direct access to tracking ID\n\n5. **DeliveredCargoConsumer.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java`)\n   - Same pattern as MisdirectedCargoConsumer\n   - Replaced JMS queue listening with Spring event listening\n\n6. **RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java`)\n   - Removed `@MessageDriven` annotation\n   - Added `@Component` for Spring management\n   - Note: This consumer doesn't have `@EventListener` yet as it appears to be triggered differently\n\n### Key Changes:\n- **Async Processing**: All event listeners use `@Async` annotation to maintain asynchronous behavior similar to JMS queues\n- **In-Process Events**: Events are now in-process Spring Application Events instead of JMS queue messages\n- **Simplified Code**: Removed JMS boilerplate (message extraction, JMSException handling)\n- **Dependency Injection**: Changed from `@Inject` to `@Autowired` for Spring compatibility\n- **Event Objects**: Created simple POJO event classes with getters for data passing\n\nThe migration maintains the same asynchronous messaging pattern while using Spring's native event system, eliminating the need for JMS infrastructure and message broker configuration."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"3dd22401-754e-4755-bfa0-ea30067f5592"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01JoibmfktLeMszEAnRfijVQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_016jyJTmPZKzfYXAV6sb17nb","name":"TodoWrite","input":{"todos":[{"content":"Write FacesConfiguration.java placeholder","status":"completed","activeForm":"Writing FacesConfiguration.java placeholder"},{"content":"Write DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java with Spring annotations","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Writing DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java with Spring annotations"},{"content":"Write assembler classes (TrackingEventsDtoAssembler, CargoStatusDtoAssembler, ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler, CargoRouteDtoAssembler, LocationDtoAssembler)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Writing assembler classes with Spring annotations"},{"content":"Write booking web beans (Booking, Track, ListCargo, ItinerarySelection, CargoDetails, ChangeDestination, ChangeDestinationDialog, ChangeArrivalDeadline, ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Writing booking web beans with Spring annotations"},{"content":"Write tracking web beans (Track, CargoTrackingViewAdapter)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Writing tracking web beans with Spring annotations"}]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":816,"cache_read_input_tokens":41963,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":816,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2131},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017tNw3GqT1JuArZd9x9DxmS","session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"7c655341-719e-4517-a9a0-b9bebe3b5f4a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01JoibmfktLeMszEAnRfijVQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01PszQVL5pLAXSJDdAuf7kT7","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.internal;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.time.LocalDate;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.stream.Collectors;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.BookingService;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.CargoRepository;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Itinerary;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.TrackingId;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.handling.HandlingEvent;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.handling.HandlingEventRepository;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.Location;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.LocationRepository;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.UnLocode;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.voyage.VoyageRepository;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.CargoRoute;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.CargoStatus;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.RouteCandidate;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.CargoRouteDtoAssembler;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.CargoStatusDtoAssembler;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.LocationDtoAssembler;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n\n@Service\npublic class DefaultBookingServiceFacade implements BookingServiceFacade, Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  @Autowired private BookingService bookingService;\n  @Autowired private LocationRepository locationRepository;\n  @Autowired private CargoRepository cargoRepository;\n  @Autowired private VoyageRepository voyageRepository;\n  @Autowired private HandlingEventRepository handlingEventRepository;\n  @Autowired private CargoRouteDtoAssembler cargoRouteDtoAssembler;\n  @Autowired private CargoStatusDtoAssembler cargoStatusDtoAssembler;\n  @Autowired private ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler itineraryCandidateDtoAssembler;\n  @Autowired private LocationDtoAssembler locationDtoAssembler;\n\n  @Override\n  public List<org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.Location>\n      listShippingLocations() {\n    List<Location> allLocations = locationRepository.findAll();\n    return locationDtoAssembler.toDtoList(allLocations);\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public String bookNewCargo(String origin, String destination, LocalDate arrivalDeadline) {\n    TrackingId trackingId =\n        bookingService.bookNewCargo(\n            new UnLocode(origin), new UnLocode(destination), arrivalDeadline);\n    return trackingId.getIdString();\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public CargoRoute loadCargoForRouting(String trackingId) {\n    Cargo cargo = cargoRepository.find(new TrackingId(trackingId));\n    return cargoRouteDtoAssembler.toDto(cargo);\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void assignCargoToRoute(String trackingIdStr, RouteCandidate routeCandidateDTO) {\n    Itinerary itinerary =\n        itineraryCandidateDtoAssembler.fromDTO(\n            routeCandidateDTO, voyageRepository, locationRepository);\n    TrackingId trackingId = new TrackingId(trackingIdStr);\n\n    bookingService.assignCargoToRoute(itinerary, trackingId);\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void changeDestination(String trackingId, String destinationUnLocode) {\n    bookingService.changeDestination(new TrackingId(trackingId), new UnLocode(destinationUnLocode));\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void changeDeadline(String trackingId, LocalDate arrivalDeadline) {\n    bookingService.changeDeadline(new TrackingId(trackingId), arrivalDeadline);\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public List<CargoRoute> listAllCargos() {\n    List<Cargo> cargos = cargoRepository.findAll();\n    List<CargoRoute> routes;\n\n    routes = cargos.stream().map(cargoRouteDtoAssembler::toDto).collect(Collectors.toList());\n\n    return routes;\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public List<String> listAllTrackingIds() {\n    List<String> trackingIds = new ArrayList<>();\n    cargoRepository\n        .findAll()\n        .forEach(cargo -> trackingIds.add(cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString()));\n\n    return trackingIds;\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public CargoStatus loadCargoForTracking(String trackingIdValue) {\n    TrackingId trackingId = new TrackingId(trackingIdValue);\n    Cargo cargo = cargoRepository.find(trackingId);\n\n    if (cargo == null) {\n      return null;\n    }\n\n    List<HandlingEvent> handlingEvents =\n        handlingEventRepository\n            .lookupHandlingHistoryOfCargo(trackingId)\n            .getDistinctEventsByCompletionTime();\n\n    return cargoStatusDtoAssembler.toDto(cargo, handlingEvents);\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public List<RouteCandidate> requestPossibleRoutesForCargo(String trackingId) {\n    List<Itinerary> itineraries =\n        bookingService.requestPossibleRoutesForCargo(new TrackingId(trackingId));\n\n    List<RouteCandidate> routeCandidates =\n        itineraries\n            .stream()\n            .map(itineraryCandidateDtoAssembler::toDto)\n            .collect(Collectors.toList());\n\n    return routeCandidates;\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":816,"cache_read_input_tokens":41963,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":816,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2131},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017tNw3GqT1JuArZd9x9DxmS","session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"07e7858a-3f93-47be-a79f-f25eeb132f83"}
