{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NkRFrFyefut5CGbMAUXgAp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n**Migration: Jakarta EE 8 -> Spring Boot 2.7.18**\n\nThe Eclipse Cargo Tracker application was fully migrated from Jakarta EE (Payara/GlassFish) to Spring Boot with embedded Tomcat. Key changes:\n\n- **~98 Java source files** migrated across domain, application, infrastructure, and interface layers\n- **EJB** (`@Stateless`, `@Singleton`, `@Startup`, `@MessageDriven`) -> Spring `@Service`, `@Component`, `@Transactional`\n- **CDI** (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) -> Spring `@Autowired`, `@Component`, `@Bean`\n- **JAX-RS** (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`) -> Spring MVC `@RestController`, `@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`\n- **JMS** (5 message-driven beans + producer) -> Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher` + `@EventListener` + `@Async`\n- **JSF/PrimeFaces** backing beans -> Spring `@Component` with `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- **Jakarta Batch** -> Spring `@Scheduled`\n- **SSE** (JAX-RS `SseBroadcaster`) -> Spring `SseEmitter`\n- **10 test files** migrated from JUnit 4 + Arquillian to JUnit 5 + `@SpringBootTest`\n\n**Build result**: Docker image builds successfully, application starts in ~5 seconds, and all 4 smoke tests pass (Application Root, Graph Traversal API, Handling Report API, SSE Cargo Tracking endpoint)."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":452,"cache_read_input_tokens":125903,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":452,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":411},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18f7ec53-4184-4cad-96bc-6843d85e3d1e","uuid":"9cc410b5-769e-465d-9e50-4f55b9f9e65c"}
